   6. Tactical Retreat: A tooltip points to the ← back arrow: "Tap here to return to the map view."
   7. Exit Strategy: Back in the macro view, a tooltip points to the "EXIT PRESENTATION" button.
   8. The Map: Out of the presentation, a tooltip points to the MAP icon on the bottom command bar: "This is where you can work on your presentation nodes."
   9. The Vault: They tap MAP, and the tooltip shifts to the DATA VAULT icon: "Ingest more raw data here to expand your Core Identity."
   10. The Gen Panel: Finally, inside the Vault, the tooltip shifts to the GEN PANEL icon: "Nodes require visual artifacts. Generate them here." Clicking this officially completes the onboarding (onboardingStep drops to 0), and the app is fully unlocked.

